            <description sparkle:format="plain-text"><![CDATA[Commit: 6b1788132f033c6eae2abfff84a05694123ac6b1
Channel: beta

fix(app): keep wallpaper playing while desktop is revealed

Focus/fullscreen playback rules sampled window geometry once, mid-animation, so revealing the desktop (click-wallpaper, F11, hot corners) left playback stuck paused. Replace the single debounce with a settling burst of re-evaluations, poll on a timer while focus rules are active, and swap the fragile desktopRevealed latch for a short reveal grace window that hands back to geometry truth.

]]></description>
